<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Trang chủ - Laptop Consultant</title>
    <link href="/css/site.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/remixicon/3.5.0/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/tailwindcss/2.2.19/tailwind.min.js"></script>
    <style>
       

        .gradient-bg {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        }

        .glass-effect {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
        }

        .card-hover {
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
        }

            .card-hover:hover {
                transform: translateY(-8px);
                box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            }

        .floating-animation {
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

       

        .fade-in {
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .fade-in-right {
            animation: fadeInRight 1s ease-out forwards;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .fade-in-left {
            animation: fadeInLeft 1s ease-out forwards;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .stagger-1 {
            animation-delay: 0.1s;
        }

        .stagger-2 {
            animation-delay: 0.2s;
        }

        .stagger-3 {
            animation-delay: 0.3s;
        }

        .stagger-4 {
            animation-delay: 0.4s;
        }

        

        .btn-primary {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

            .btn-primary::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: -100%;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.2), transparent);
                transition: left 0.5s;
            }

            .btn-primary:hover::before {
                left: 100%;
            }

        .primary-color {
            color: #667eea;
        }

        .bg-primary {
            background-color: #667eea;
        }

        .border-primary {
            border-color: #667eea;
        }

        .text-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .hero-pattern {
            background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(circle at 75% 75%, rgba(118, 75, 162, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
        }

        .laptop-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fafc 100%);
            border: 1px solid rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
        }

        .price-highlight {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .icon-glow {
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3));
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="bg-white relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden hero-pattern">
        <!-- Decorative Elements -->
        <div class="absolute top-20 left-10 w-32 h-32 bg-purple-200 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 floating-animation"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-40 right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-blue-200 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 floating-animation" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-20 w-32 h-32 bg-pink-200 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70 floating-animation" style="animation-delay: 4s;"></div>

        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20">
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center">
                <!-- Left Content -->
                <div class="lg:w-1/2 mb-12 lg:mb-0 fade-in-left">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
                            Tìm laptop
                            <span class="text-gradient">phù hợp</span>
                            với bạn
                        </h1>
                        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
                            Hệ thống tư vấn thông minh với AI giúp bạn tìm chiếc laptop hoàn hảo trong vài phút.
                        </p>

                        <!-- CTA Buttons -->
                        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4">
                            <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Laptop")" class="btn-primary bg-primary text-white px-6 py-2 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors text-sm btn-primary bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-purple-600 transition-all duration-300 text-lg font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
                                <i class="ri-robot-line mr-2"></i>
                                Tư vấn ngay
                            </a>
                            <a href="@Url.Action("Compare", "Laptop")" class="text-white btn-primary bg-white text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 border-primary hover:bg-purple-50 transition-all duration-300 text-lg font-semibold">
                                <i class="ri-scales-line mr-2"></i>
                                So sánh laptop
                            </a>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Stats -->
                        <div class="flex space-x-8 mt-12">
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gradient">1000+</div>
                                <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Laptop được tư vấn</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gradient">98%</div>
                                <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Khách hàng hài lòng</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-gradient">24/7</div>
                                <div class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Hỗ trợ tư vấn</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Right Content -->
                <div class="lg:w-1/2 relative fade-in-right">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <!-- Main Laptop Image -->
                        <div class="relative z-10 floating-animation">
                            <div class="glass-effect rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl">
                                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1496181133206-80ce9b88a853?w=600&h=400&fit=crop&crop=center"
                                     alt="Modern Laptop"
                                     class="w-full h-auto object-cover rounded-2xl">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Floating Cards -->
                        <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 glass-effect rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-lg floating-animation" style="animation-delay: 1s;">
                            <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
                                <span class="text-sm font-medium">AI đang phân tích...</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 glass-effect rounded-2xl p-4 shadow-lg floating-animation" style="animation-delay: 2s;">
                            <div class="text-center">
                                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-gradient">4.9★</div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-gray-600">Đánh giá trung bình</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <!-- Section Header -->
            <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
                <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
                    Laptop <span class="text-gradient">nổi bật</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                    Khám phá những mẫu laptop được yêu thích nhất với công nghệ tiên tiến và thiết kế hiện đại.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Laptop Grid -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                @{
                    var staggerClasses = new[] { "stagger-1", "stagger-2", "stagger-3" };
                    var badgeStyles = new[]
                    {
                                "bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500",
                                "bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500",
                                "bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500",
                                "bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-teal-500",
                                "bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-orange-500"
                                };
                    var badges = new[] { "Nổi bật", "Mới nhất", "Gaming", "Văn phòng", "Cao cấp" };
                    var index = 0;
                }

                @foreach (var laptop in Model)
                {
                    var staggerClass = staggerClasses[index % staggerClasses.Length];
                    var badgeStyle = badgeStyles[index % badgeStyles.Length];
                    var badge = badges[index % badges.Length];

                    <div class="laptop-card rounded-3xl overflow-hidden card-hover fade-in @staggerClass">
                        <div class="relative">
                            <img src="@laptop.ImageUrl"
                                 alt="@laptop.Name"
                                 class="w-full h-64 object-cover">
                            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 @badgeStyle text-white text-sm font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full shadow-lg">
                                @badge
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="p-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">@laptop.Name</h4>

                            <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
                                <div class="flex items-center">
                                    <i class="ri-cpu-line text-primary mr-3 text-lg icon-glow"></i>
                                    <span class="text-gray-700">@laptop.CPU</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center">
                                    <i class="ri-hard-drive-line text-primary mr-3 text-lg icon-glow"></i>
                                    <span class="text-gray-700">@laptop.RAM, @laptop.Storage</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center">
                                    <i class="ri-computer-line text-primary mr-3 text-lg icon-glow"></i>
                                    <span class="text-gray-700">@laptop.Screen</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                <span class="text-2xl font-bold price-highlight">@laptop.Price.ToString("N0") ₫</span>
                                <div class="flex space-x-2">
                                    <form asp-action="SelectForCompare" method="get" class="inline">
                                        <input type="hidden" name="laptopId" value="@laptop.Id" />
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary bg-gray-100 text-primary p-3 rounded-full hover:bg-purple-50 transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">
                                            <i class="text-white ri-scales-line text-lg"></i>
                                        </button>
                                    </form>
                                    <a href="@Url.Action("Details", "Laptop", new { id = laptop.Id })" class="btn-primary bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-purple-600 transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg font-semibold">
                                        Chi tiết
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    index++;
                }

                <!-- View All Button -->
                <div class="text-center mt-12 fade-in stagger-4">
                    <a href="@Url.Action("Compare", "Laptop")" class="btn-primary bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl hover:from-purple-600 hover:to-pink-600 transition-all duration-300 text-lg font-semibold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
                        <i class="ri-eye-line mr-2"></i>
                        Xem tất cả laptop
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
                <h3 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Tại sao chọn chúng tôi?</h3>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Trải nghiệm tư vấn laptop thông minh với công nghệ AI tiên tiến
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg card-hover fade-in stagger-1">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <i class="ri-robot-line text-3xl text-white"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">AI Thông Minh</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        Hệ thống AI học hỏi từ hàng ngàn trường hợp tư vấn để đưa ra gợi ý phù hợp nhất.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg card-hover fade-in stagger-2">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <i class="ri-time-line text-3xl text-white"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Nhanh Chóng</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        Chỉ trong vài phút, bạn sẽ có danh sách laptop phù hợp với nhu cầu và ngân sách.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-lg card-hover fade-in stagger-3">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-teal-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <i class="ri-shield-check-line text-3xl text-white"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Đáng Tin Cậy</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                        Thông tin laptop được cập nhật liên tục từ các nguồn chính thức và đáng tin cậy.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>